Initial commit: System maintenance scripts suite

- Add comprehensive README with environment-loading setup
- Include troubleshooting guide and script usage documentation
- Add all maintenance scripts with proper environment configuration
- Include Raycast integration scripts for quick access
- Add .gitignore for proper repository management

Features:
✅ Automated weekly maintenance via launchd
✅ Individual script execution with logging
✅ Environment variable preservation with bash -l
✅ Comprehensive error handling and troubleshooting
✅ Development environment maintenance (npm, pip, gems, etc.)
✅ System cleanup and optimization
✅ Document backup with timestamp archiving
✅ Package updates for macOS and Homebrew
